Dish Dashboard — Full Stack Project (MERN)

A full-stack dish management dashboard built using MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js (MERN).
This project allows users to:

View all dishes

Add new dishes using images stored in the backend

Toggle Published / Unpublished status

View image previews

Maintain a clean dish database with real-time UI updates after actions

Dish/
│
├── backend/
│   ├── public/
