    ├── index.html
    ├── vite.config.js
    └── package.json


Features
✔ Backend
MongoDB database for storing dish records
REST API built with Express.js
Routes for:
Get all dishes
Add a new dish
Toggle publish/unpublish
Fetch available images
Static file serving for dish images
Seed script to populate database

✔ Frontend
Built using React + Vite
Dashboard to display all dishes
Add dish form with:
Image dropdown
Preview of selected image
Publish/unpublish checkbox
Publish toggle button with immediate updates
Fallback image support
